                    </div>
                </div>

                <h3 class="faq-subcategory-title">Staying Healthy &amp; Fit</h3>
                <div class="faq-list">
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                            What routine is best for overall health?
                            <span class="faq-icon"></span>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">2 to 3 weight training sessions per week combined with some cardio is enough to maintain good health. The AI coach creates balanced programs tailored to this goal.</div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                            I&rsquo;m over 40, is strength training still effective?
                            <span class="faq-icon"></span>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">Absolutely! Strength training is actually recommended after 40 to fight age-related muscle loss. The AI coach adapts intensity and volume to your profile.</div></div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="faq-item">
                        <button class="faq-question" onclick="this.parentElement.classList.toggle('open')">
                            Do I need to train every day?
                            <span class="faq-icon"></span>
                        </button>
                        <div class="faq-answer"><div class="faq-answer-inner">No, rest is essential for progress. 3 to 5 sessions per week with rest days is sufficient. AIVancePro incorporates recovery into your planning.</div></div>
